# Prepare the single frame.
# =========================

# Adds variance arrays, subtracts the bias, differences chopped beams,
# and adds world co-ordinate system.
     _PREPARE_SINGLE_FRAME_

# Podule
# ======

=head1 NAME

_MAKE_BPM_HELLO_ -- Sets up data-reduction tasks and data for MAKE_BPM recipes.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

The script performs the following tasks.

=over 4

=item *

Performs the standard per-frame preparation tasks.  See
L<_PREPARE_SINGLE_FRAME_|_PREPARE_SINGLE_FRAME_> for more details.

=back

=head1 NOTES

=over 4

=item *

This primitive is suitable for imaging instruments.

=back

